<HEADLINE>
AMENDMENT TO ANTI-DISCRIMINATION LAW PASSED
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Taipei, May 5 (CNA) 05/05/07  15:52:46 (By Ruth Wang)
</P>
<P>
The Legislative Yuan passed an amendment Friday to the Employment
Services Law to prohibit job discrimination on the basis of three
more categories -- age, birth place and sexual orientation -- to
better protect equal employment opportunities, a Council of Labor
